snippet.title: SNAILS official trailer #1
snippet.description:
"SNAILS" is a retro-themed 3-D Beat'em up designed to mimic the characteristics and appearance of a late-90's PS1 game.


The game is currently available for purchase on itch.io for $2.99 USD, at the following link:


https://tpole.itch.io/snails
